{"type": "article", "id": 30053, "title": "极简挂钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-24T22:51:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160724230625Uw8EXVZucIjBQ9HK.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>澳大利亚设计师 <a href=\"http://abialice.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Abi Alice</a> 为知名家用品品牌 <a href=\"http://www.alessi.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alessi</a> 打造了两款各具特色的挂钟 Dotty 和 Infinity。Dotty 的设计灵感来源于文具店内的那些五颜六色粘点，Alice 将圆形与直线搭配在一起打造出了极简的风格，而且会让人联想到古时通过观察天体运动确定时间的天文装置。Infinity 则采用了层层叠叠的几何结构，反映着时间不断变化永不停息的特质，摒弃了数字符号的表面只有两根蓝色的指针，有一种点睛之笔的感觉。<a href=\"http://store.alessi.com/usa/en-gb/catalog/detail/dotty-clock-wall-clock/abi11?ic=ujLeKA%3D%3D\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dotty</a> 和 <a href=\"http://store.alessi.com/usa/en-gb/catalog/detail/infinity-clock-wall-clock/abi10?ic=ZWVY%2Fg%3D%3D\" rel=\"nofollow\">Infinity</a> 的价格分别为 150 和 220 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242306350nUeAcPYvyGF4QIr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724230635rYh7RSyb68OnNesu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724230635bC6x4QfWhkTANIe8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724230635oghYMEJBTKpbXPzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}